The Music Shop said it signed astock option agreement with the &lt;Saxon Co> calling for it toreceive 100,000 dlrs in return for 210 mln shares and an optionfor Saxon to buy additional common stock for up to 400,000dlrs.    The company also said it will hold a special shareholders'meeting April 15 to vote on a proposed one-for-100 sharereverse split.    Saxon is a venture capital firm from Dallas, the companysaid. Reuter&#3;